---
---
<footer class="bg-brazil-blue text-white">
  <div class="flag-stripe"></div>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #009C3B 50%, #FFDF00 50%);"></div>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl" data-lang-content="en">BrazilRemit</span>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl" data-lang-content="zh">巴西汇款</span>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl" data-lang-content="pt">BrazilRemit</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="en">Your trusted guide for Brazil international remittance information.</p>
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="zh">您信赖的巴西国际汇款资讯指南。</p>
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-lang-content="pt">Seu guia confiável de informações sobre remessas internacionais do Brasil.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-brazil-yellow mb-4">
          <span data-lang-content="en">Quick Links</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">快速链接</span>
          <span data-lang-content="pt">Links Rápidos</span>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-200">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <span data-lang-content="en">Home</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">首页</span>
            <span data-lang-content="pt">Início</span>
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <span data-lang-content="en">About Us</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">关于我们</span>
            <span data-lang-content="pt">Sobre Nós</span>
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/today-brazil" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <span data-lang-content="en">Today's Brazil</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">今日巴西</span>
            <span data-lang-content="pt">Brasil Hoje</span>
          </a></li>
          <li><a href="/faq" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">
            <span data-lang-content="en">FAQ</span>
            <span data-lang-content="zh">常见问题</span>
            <span data-lang-content="pt">FAQ</span>
          </a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Remittance Links -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-brazil-yellow mb-4">
          <span data-lang-content="en">Remittance</span>
          <span data-lang-content="zh">汇款目的地</span>
          <span data-lang-content="pt">Remessas</span>
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-blue-200">
          <li><a href="/remittance/usa" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇺🇸 EUA / USA</a></li>
          <li><a href="/remittance/china" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇨🇳 China</a></li>
          <li><a href="/remittance/hong-kong" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇭🇰 Hong Kong</a></li>
          <li><a href="/remittance/uk" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇬🇧 Reino Unido / UK</a></li>
          <li><a href="/remittance/singapore" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇸🇬 Singapura / Singapore</a></li>
          <li><a href="/remittance/japan" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">🇯🇵 Japão / Japan</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-blue-700 mt-10 pt-6">
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-300 mb-3" data-lang-content="en">
        This website provides informational content only. Exchange rates and fees are subject to change. Always verify with your chosen service provider before making transfers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-300 mb-3" data-lang-content="zh">
        本网站仅提供资讯内容。汇率和费用可能随时变化。在进行转账前，请务必向您选择的服务提供商核实。
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-300 mb-3" data-lang-content="pt">
        Este site fornece apenas conteúdo informativo. As taxas de câmbio e tarifas estão sujeitas a alterações. Sempre verifique com o provedor de serviços escolhido antes de fazer transferências.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-blue-400">
        © {new Date().getFullYear()} BrazilRemit.
        <span data-lang-content="en"> All rights reserved.</span>
        <span data-lang-content="zh"> 版权所有。</span>
        <span data-lang-content="pt"> Todos os direitos reservados.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
